videos.description: Boston College's Ky Bowman picks off a Notre Dame pass and takes it himself for an and-1 layup at the other end.
videos.headline: Boston College gets and-1 to fall in transition

videos.description: Notre Dame's Temple Gibbs forces a Boston College turnover and assists V.J. Beachem on a powerful dunk.
videos.headline: Notre Dame turns a steal into a two-handed slam

videos.description: Notre Dame's Martinas Geben stops Boston College's alley oop attempt.
videos.headline: Geben rejects alley-oop attempt

videos.description: Notre Dame's Matt Farrell gets a steal and Rex Pflufeger knocks down the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's defense leads to 3-pointer

videos.description: Notre Dame's Bonzi Colson fully extends to get the offensive rebound, sinks the basket and draws the foul.
videos.headline: Colson extends to get the rebound and the basket

videos.description: Notre Dame's Martinas Geben takes out anger on the rim with a vicious putback dunk.
videos.headline: Geben puts back strong dunk

videos.description: Notre Dame senior Patrick Mazza with the emphatic dunk to help cap off an impressive win against Boston College as the bench goes crazy.
videos.headline: Notre Dame senior seals it for the Fighting Irish
